															<p>Give the Office of the Superintendent of Public Instruction a call or E-mail.<br />
Their number is (360) 725-6075 or <a href="mailto:speced@ospi.wednet.edu" rel="nofollow">speced@ospi.wednet.edu</a> .They are pretty good at answering questions and letting you know who you need to talk to about the situation. Also you might want to look at Washington law site for special education laws apps.legwa.gov/wac/default.aspx?cite=392-172 .Good luck-</p>
